## ğŸ“¦ Features

- ğŸ” **Read** and parse recipe bytes into usable structured data.
- âœï¸ **serialize** the recipe back into bytes for easy injection or saving.
- âš™ï¸ Supports known structure fields (appearance, gear, etc.)
- ğŸ§ª Designed for modding, analysis, and custom content pipelines.

